data.description: Charming country home close to the city at the end of a cul-de-sac. Located in NW Porterville near 2 new home subdivisions. On 3.69 acres. with a large shop, and PAID SOLAR. As you enter this 4 bedroom 3 bath house there is beautiful wood look flooring. The kitchen offers tile countertops, shaker cabinets, with a lot of cabinet storage. So  much space with so many possibilities. Landscaped front yard, lots of trees and fruit trees, with views of the hills, a water feature, and lighted flag pole. Schedule you showing today.
